<p class="">He was a Tory; be careful.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e0dc7725-ccd3-4a04-a912-3a6f6af308d3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-17/debates/1d5b6183-9355-476b-99b6-f56659a464c4/IronAndSteelBill#contribution-e0dc7725-ccd3-4a04-a912-3a6f6af308d3">
