<p class="">What would a nationalised industry do in that case?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6477f2a5-92ff-4a10-b090-57b645038ed5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
